column2: select OS.objID, OS.clean, OS.u, OS.g, OS.r, OS.i , OS.z, OS.u_err, OS.g_err, OS.r_err, OS.i_err, OS.z_err, OS.ra, OS.dec, OS.ra_err, OS.dec_err, OS.RowNumber from (select objID, clean, psfMag_u - extinction_u as u, psfMag_g - extinction_g as g, psfMag_r - extinction_R as r, psfMag_i - extinction_i as i, psfMag_z - extinction_z as z, psfMagErr_u as u_err, psfMagErr_g as g_err, psfMagErr_r as r_err, psfMagErr_i as i_err, psfMagErr_z as z_err, ra, dec, raErr as ra_err, decErr as dec_err, ROW_NUMBER () over (order by dec) as RowNumber from star) as OS where OS.RowNumber % # = # AND OS.CLEAN = # AND OS.ra BETWEEN # AND # AND OS.dec BETWEEN # AND # AND OS.psfMag_r < # AND OS.psfMag_g < #
